job.title: Gauhati High Court Gr-I Assam Judicial Service Exam Recruitment 2021 – Apply Online for 12 Vacancies in Assam
job.body:
Total Vacancies: 12

Name of the Posts:

  • Gauhati High Court Gr-I Assam Judicial Service Exam

Description

New Assam Government Jobs have been published by Gauhati High Court for the posts of Judicial Service. If you are finding a government job in Assam then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for these posts in Assam, from

06-05-2021, and till the 24-05-2021. If you are interested in all these posts in Assam and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.


Application fee:

  • The mode of application is Online
  • The application fee for SC/ ST Candidates is only: Rs. 250/-.
  • The application fee for PWD (Locomotor Disability) Candidates is only: Nil.
  • The application fee for All Others Candidates is only: RS. 500/-

Educational qualification to apply for GHCJudicial Service posts in Assam:

  • To apply for a Judicial Service post in Assam, your Degree (Law) must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates:

  •  The starting date to apply for these posts is 06-05-2021.
  •  The last date to apply in these posts is 24-05-2021 

Age Limit Criteria:

  • The minimum age should be 35 years.
  • The maximum age should be 45 years.

GHCJudicial Service Pay Scale:

  • According to the information given by the Assam Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is ₹ 44,770  

How to apply for Gauhati High Court Gr-I Assam Judicial Service Exam Recruitment 2021.

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of these posts in Assam. Fill in your details and submit it

  • Or follow all the steps given below,
  •  First, go to the official website of Gauhati High Court and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked BY Gauhati High Court 
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.
